    public class CopyOnWriteIDataMap
extends IDataMap
implements java.lang.Cloneable, java.io.Serializable
    Wraps an IData in an IData and Map compatible wrapper that makes copies of the wrapped IData and its nested IData children when they are written to.

      • normalize

        private static java.lang.Object normalize(java.lang.Object value)
        Converts the given value if it is an IData or IData[] compatible object to a CopyOnWriteIDataMap or CopyOnWriteIDataMap[] respectively.
        Parameters:
        value - The value to be normalized.
        Returns:
        If the value is an IData or IData[] compatible object, a new CopyOnWriteIDataMap or CopyOnWriteIDataMap[] respectively is returned which wraps the given value, otherwise the value itself is returned unmodified.
